  "Description": {
    "English": "A luxury firework, rich in magnesium and indium. Ignite to create glittering displays in the sky.<br><br>Place launch tube via the <VAL_ON>Build Menu<> (<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>). <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warning</span>: Aim away from living creatures. Not recommended for indoor use.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一枚包含大量镁和铟的奢华烟花。点燃就可以在天空中开启一场炫丽的光影表演。<br><br>可以通过<VAL_ON>建造菜单<>（<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>）来放置发射筒。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：不可瞄准活体生物。不建议在室内使用。",
    "TencentChinese": "一枚包含大量镁和铟的奢华烟花。点燃就可以在天空中开启一场炫丽的光影表演。<br><br>可以通过<VAL_ON>建造菜单<>（<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>）来放置发射筒。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：不可瞄准活体生物。不建议在室内使用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "豪華煙火，富含鎂與銦。點燃即可在天空中創造出絢爛效果。<br><br>可從<VAL_ON>建造選單<>（<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>）放置發射管。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：請勿對著生物發射，不建議於室內使用。"
  },
